cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CR 

This paper is likely to belong to the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with adversarial training of machine learning algorithms. It also involves optimization problems, which could place it in the categories of cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of deep learning techniques and the focus on convergence speed could also place it in the categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
